column1: We’ve been socially distancing ourselves for many months now. With the holidays right around the corner it is imperative we continue to do our part to help suppress the Coronavirus. It’s important that we continue to take necessary precautions to prevent the spread of the COVID.
Mr. President we all want a booming economy.  But it’s impossible to be good on the economy and bad on Coronavirus.
